snippet.title: Paper Mario 64K | v3.7.0 Progress Report (Texture Pack - Refolded)
snippet.description:
The texture pack is becoming huge at 4K with each update!
Remember this pack is still in progress so changes might happen.
Thank you for your support!

Release date:
Patrons (4K): Available for Adventurers and Legends (March 18, 2024 - Supporters)
Public (HD): March 21, 2024 (White outline version)
